ClassDesc: Interface to be implemented by UI component to support seeking. PlaybackGlueHost may implement the interface to support seeking UI for the PlaybackGlue. There is only one single method @B_android#support#v17#leanback#widget#PlaybackSeekUi#setPlaybackSeekUiClient_E@ in the interface. Client (PlaybackGlue) registers itself as a Client to receive events emitted by PlaybackSeekUi and provide data to the PlaybackSeekUi.
